@page "/faq"

<PageTitle>FAQ</PageTitle>

<Div Flex="Flex.Row">
    <Div Flex="Flex.Column" Margin="Margin.Is3" Padding="Padding.Is4.FromTop">
        <div class="d-flex flex-row gap-3">
            <div class="bg-danger" style="height: 50px; width: 5px;"></div>
            <h1 class="fw-bold">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
        </div>
        <Paragraph TextSize="TextSize.ExtraLarge">
            <span class="fw-bold">1. What is Your Blog?</span>
            <p>Your Blog is a blogging platform that offers engaging and insightful content across a variety of topics, including the latest trends, personal growth advice, tech updates, and lifestyle hacks.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">2. How can I create an account?</span>
            <p>To create an account, click on the "Sign Up" button at the top right corner of the homepage. Fill in the required information, including your name, email address, and a password. Once submitted, you will receive a confirmation email to verify your account.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">3. How do I reset my password?</span>
            <p>If you've forgotten your password, click on the "Forgot Password" link on the login page. Enter your registered email address, and you will receive instructions on how to reset your password via email.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">4. How can I subscribe to the newsletter?</span>
            <p>To subscribe to our newsletter, enter your email address in the subscription box located at the bottom of our homepage or any blog post page. You will receive regular updates about new articles, special features, and promotions.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">5. How do I submit a guest post?</span>
            <p>We welcome guest posts from writers who have unique insights to share. To submit a guest post, please visit our "Write for Us" page and follow the guidelines provided. Submit your article via the submission form or email it to your-blog@blog.ro. Our editorial team will review your submission and get back to you.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">6. How can I contact customer support?</span>
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, you can contact our customer support team by emailing your-blog@blog.ro or calling 0251010101. Our support team is available Monday through Friday from [business hours].</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">7. How do I report inappropriate content?</span>
            <p>If you come across any content that you believe violates our terms and conditions or is inappropriate, please report it to us by clicking the "Report" button next to the content or by emailing us at your-blog@blog.ro with the details of the issue.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">8. Can I advertise on Your Blog?</span>
            <p>Yes, we offer various advertising opportunities on Your Blog. For more information about our advertising options, please visit our "Advertise with Us" page or contact our advertising team at your-blog@blog.ro.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">9. How do I unsubscribe from the newsletter?</span>
            <p>If you wish to unsubscribe from our newsletter, click the "Unsubscribe" link at the bottom of any newsletter email you receive from us. You will be redirected to a page where you can confirm your unsubscription.</p>

            <span class="fw-bold">10. How can I update my account information?</span>
            <p>To update your account information, log in to your account and go to the "Account Settings" page. Here, you can update your personal information, change your password, and manage your email preferences.</p>

            <p>If you have any other questions not covered here, feel free to contact us at your-blog@blog.ro.</p>

            <p>Thank you for visiting Your Blog!</p>
        </Paragraph>
    </Div>
</Div>